commands.name: az boards iteration project create
commands.syntax:
az boards iteration project create --name
                                   [--detect {false, true}]
                                   [--finish-date]
                                   [--org]
                                   [--path]
                                   [--project]
                                   [--start-date]

commands.name: az boards iteration project delete
commands.syntax:
az boards iteration project delete --path
                                   [--detect {false, true}]
                                   [--org]
                                   [--project]
                                   [--yes]

commands.name: az boards iteration project list
commands.syntax:
az boards iteration project list [--depth]
                                 [--detect {false, true}]
                                 [--org]
                                 [--path]
                                 [--project]

commands.name: az boards iteration project show
commands.summary: Show iteration details for a project.
commands.syntax:
az boards iteration project show --id
                                 [--detect {false, true}]
                                 [--org]
                                 [--project]

commands.name: az boards iteration project update
commands.syntax:
az boards iteration project update --path
                                   [--child-id]
                                   [--detect {false, true}]
                                   [--finish-date]
                                   [--name]
                                   [--org]
                                   [--project]
                                   [--start-date]
